    "v3": "For peaceful homes and healthful days, For all the blessings earth displays, We owe Thee thankfulness and praise, Who givest all.",
    "v4": "Thou didst not spare Thine only Son, But gav&#39;st Him for a world undone, And freely, with that blessèd One, Thou givest all.",
    "v5": "Thou giv&#39;st the Spirit&#39;s blessèd dow&#39;r, Spirit of life and love and pow&#39;r, And dost His sev&#39;nfold graces show&#39;r Upon us all."
